Subject: drm/nouveau/kms/nv50-: Report possible_crtcs incorrectly on mstos,
 for now
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 481404957a14f9c46576913ba12985e6798b7d32
